  "text": "Smooth bromegrass and meadow bromegrass may be successfully crossed to produce hybrid bromegrass [CITATION_1] [6] [CITATION_2] . The interspecific hybrid expresses characteristics of both parents and has shown potential for hay during spring and for pasture during the summer and autumn [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] .",
